    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and totally ready to hit the road for its next adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so you\u2019re getting a great car that still has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take a look, I'd love for it to go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1), a driver-focused specimen featuring the 3.8L M97.01 horizontally opposed flat-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant is mated to a 6-speed G97 manual transaxle, providing tactile gear engagement via a factory short-throw shifter. The vehicle is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), featuring a 10mm lower ride height and electronically controlled damping for superior roll stiffness. Recent mechanical maintenance includes a preventative water pump replacement and a full diagnostic scan confirming zero over-rev events in Range 4-6. The chassis remains rigid, supported by 19-inch staggered alloy wheels and a dual-mass flywheel that ensures smooth torque delivery. While the cabin reflects the honest patina of a well-utilized grand tourer, the mechanical vitals\u2014including oil pressure and thermal management\u2014are within factory specifications. This is a robust, high-performance platform ready for technical mountain passes or spirited daily use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained, reliable performer that still carries a premium presence on the road. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather seating is free of tears or heavy stains, showing only the natural softening and light creasing expected of a car that has been enjoyed. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium sound system, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is sound and has been serviced at regular intervals; the engine pulls strong and the transmission shifts smoothly through every gear. We recently performed a multi-point inspection, and the brakes and tires show significant life remaining. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been cared for by a non-smoker and is ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated to meet exacting standards of performance and presentation. It features a meticulously maintained powertrain and a refined interior that reflects a history of responsible ownership. This offering represents an exceptional balance of reliability and sophistication, providing a superior driving experience for the discerning professional who demands quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
