      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go and runs like a dream! I've taken great care of it, so you're getting a fantastic vehicle that still has tons of life left. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
