      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to maintain optimal variable valve timing. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, currently fitted with Bilstein dampers for enhanced lateral stability. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a fresh set of staggered Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a driver-focused example with excellent mechanical vitals, ready for the apex.",
